{"tid":1451151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要贏 就要Be Tsunami","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T07:55:41.000Z","uid":302,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c04fe60ab5be055ab9a0999347694418d8f382a7","tid":1451151,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:50.000Z","msg":"Be Water已經唔再合適<br />\n當時戰術係人地唔會主動出擊 只會整條封鎖線 然後放TG驅散<br />\n所以留低冇用 同衝唔散人地一排防線 更莫講話當時大家未夠膽 同心理仲未升級<br />\n但而家人地係突進 亂9拉人 不留手打人 <br />\n佢地而家好多時係冇隊形 所以一定要反攻 !<br />\n<br />\n敵駐我擾 敵進我撲 敵退我追 敵疲我打 ！！<br />\n<br />\nbye bye popo<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.temblor.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Japanese-Tsunami-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.temblor.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FJapanese-Tsunami-3.jpg&h=a31a741f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee658cc094a2370157d15ce61f8ce6bfab1facc8","tid":1451151,"uid":302,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:56.000Z","msg":"Be Tsunami<br />\n敵駐我擾 敵進我撲 敵退我追 敵疲我打 ！！"},{"pid":"84b7eab4eaf2faeda9d3ab99faabeca7977f0d2c","tid":1451151,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:28:33.000Z","msg":"我地有既係集體意識 共同信念<br />\nBe Tsunami<br />\n敵駐我擾 敵進我撲 敵退我追 敵疲我打 ！！"},{"pid":"a00fc10b0a610c3a63bb569546ac68d14fcdfe7d","tid":1451151,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"見到popo 一齊湧上去！"},{"pid":"8c8802e2252239cf7d2be2b4c085468aee81a1a2","tid":1451151,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:29:50.000Z","msg":"我地不嬲都只係得一個優勢 就係人多"},{"pid":"3e81db2451b86d16e352b72bffa8b25a2b645b79","tid":1451151,"uid":74099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:30:08.000Z","msg":"2019年 721、811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n<br />\n812 <br />\n不塞鐵 <br />\n機